      "committer": {
        "name": "ARD0NIZ",
        "email": "96878771+ARD0NIZ@users.noreply.github.com",
        "date": "2026-05-04T10:10:13Z"
      },
      "message": "feat: Add permission checks for Manage Server in security and leveling settings\n\n- Implemented permission checks for Manage Server in security settings to ensure only users with the appropriate permissions can modify security settings.\n- Added similar permission checks in leveling settings to restrict access to users with Manage Server permission.\n- Enhanced logging commands to check for channel permissions before sending messages to the log channels.\n- Updated moderation commands (ban, kick, clear, timeout) to verify the existence of a moderation log channel and required permissions before executing actions.\n- Improved error handling and user feedback for missing permissions and unconfigured log channels. #deploy",
